---
import Main from "../layouts/Main.astro";
---

<Main title="Beyond technology">
  <div class="beyond-tech_container">
    <h1 class="about-me">About me</h1>

    <p class="first_paragraph">
      I live in Montevideo, Uruguay, more precisely on the west side of town. I
      live with my partner and my two wonderful cats <span class="Milo"
        >Milo</span
      > and <span class="Ares">Ares.</span>
    </p>
    <section class="container">
      <div class="slider-wrapper">
        <div class="slider">
          <img
            src="../AresyMilo1.webp"
            alt="Photo of my beloved mascots"
            id="slide-1"
          />
          <img
            src="../AresyMilo2.webp"
            alt="Photo of my beloved mascots"
            id="slide-2"
          />
          <img
            src="../AresyMilo3.webp"
            alt="Photo of my beloved mascots"
            id="slide-3"
          />
          <div class="slider-nav">
            <a href="#slide-1" no></a>
            <a href="#slide-2"></a>
            <a href="#slide-3"></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <p>
      When I'm not on my computer I like to take care of my <span class="Plants"
        >plants</span
      >, throughout my childhood taking care of plants have been a part of my
      life. My mother taught me how to, she had a little farm back then so I
      grew up in an amazing natural environment
    </p>

    <p>
      If I'm not taking care of the <span class="Plants">plants</span> or playing
      with my cats. I could be playing video games or studying something that caught
      my attention. I've always liked to learn new things, but now that I'm growing
      in IT learning is something that I try to do everyday, we all know how technology
      grows each day. So, to me it is really important to stay up to date with the
      latest news.
    </p>
  </div>
</Main>

<style>
  h1 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 5rem;
  }
  p {
    margin: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .first_paragraph {
    margin-top: -1rem;
  }

  .Ares,
  .Milo,
  .Plants {
    font-weight: bolder;
    font-size: large;
  }

  .Ares {
    color: orange;
  }
  .Milo {
    color: grey;
  }
  .Plants {
    color: green;
  }
  .salute {
    font-weight: bolder;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
  }
  .about-me {
    color: orangered;
  }

  .container {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .slider-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .slider {
    display: flex;
    aspect-ratio: 16/11;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    box-shadow: 0 1.5rem 3rem -0.75rem hsla(0, 0%, 0%, 0.25);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }
  .slider img {
    object-fit: cover;
    flex: 1 0 100%;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
  }
  .slider-nav {
    display: flex;
    column-gap: 1rem;
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 1;
    bottom: 1.25rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }
  .slider a {
    width: 0.5rem;
    height: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: #fff;
    opacity: 0.75;
    transition: opacity ease 250ms;
  }
  .slider-nav a:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .slider-wrapper {
      max-width: 95vw; /* Further adjust max-width */
    }

    .slider {
      aspect-ratio: 4/3; /* Adjust aspect ratio for smaller screens */
    }

    .slider-nav {
      bottom: 0.75rem; /* Reduce bottom spacing on smaller screens */
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .slider-nav {
      column-gap: 0.5rem; /* Reduce gap between navigation dots */
    }
  }
</style>
